---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="AI Code Academy's terms of service and conditions of use."
>
  <div class="container legal-content">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <section class="policy-section matrix-shadow">
      <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing our website and services, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions, all applicable laws and regulations, and agree that you are responsible for compliance with any applicable local laws.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section matrix-shadow">
      <h2>2. Course Access</h2>
      <p>Upon enrollment and payment, you will receive access to the course materials for the duration specified in the course description. Access rights are personal and non-transferable.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section matrix-shadow">
      <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content, including but not limited to course materials, videos, code examples, and documentation, is the property of AI Code Academy and is protected by intellectual property laws.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section matrix-shadow">
      <h2>4. User Conduct</h2>
      <p>You agree to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Not share your account credentials</li>
        <li>Not redistribute course materials</li>
        <li>Maintain professional conduct in all interactions</li>
        <li>Use the platform for its intended educational purpose</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-content {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .policy-section {
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background-color: rgba(71, 212, 105, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  li::before {
    content: ">";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--brand-color);
  }
</style>